_Wireless Frequencies_  стандарты  band !!!!
standard 		band(ghz) 		maximum Bandwidth             transmission       maximum range
				 диапозон ГГЦ    пропускная способность			method          in=inddors out=outdoors

1 802.11 			2.4 gnz  	1 mbps of 2 mbps   				dsss or fhss       20m in 100m out

2 802.11a            5 ghz 	 		54mbps 							ofdm           35m in 120m out

3 802.11b 			2,4 ghz 		11 mbps 						DSSS           32m in 140m out

4 802.11g             2,4 ghz 	     54 mbps                        ofdm or dsss   32m in 140m out

5 802.11n			2,4 5, both      300 mbps                         ofdm          70m in 250m out
									channel banding 
6 802.11ac				5 			3gbps 							ofdm            70m in 250m out 
