Section 4: TCP/IP Model
_TCP/IP Model_
4 layers 

OSI MODEL         TCP/IP Model

7 Application    4 Application
6 Prsentation 
5 Session 

4 Transport      3 Transport  

3 Network        2 Internet

2 Data link      1 Network interface 
1 Physical

